Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:06.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那孩子又变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}光芒更加璀璨夺目了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:13.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但仍有阻碍他发光污浊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:17.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那孩子还会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}迟早会强大到能消除污浊的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:27.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不冒险就无法破壳而出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}交给你了 奥塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起 忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:24.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}吓我一跳 没想到你还会变身的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:28.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以只要这个能力不为人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没有人会认为现在的莉莉是以前那个莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要消失一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他们就会以为我死在地下城了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:39.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不过莉莉觉得这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:44.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要贝尔大人知道这点 莉莉就心满意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:49.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}比起这个 贝尔大人觉得这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我欺骗了贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:58.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}利用了贝尔大人的好意 背叛了您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就这样被原谅的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:03.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:14.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我是莉莉露卡·亚蒂 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你就是传闻中的支援者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔已经告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我下楼去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不过杯子好像只有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么嘛 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我和贝尔用一个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人也偶尔会开这样的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么 先让我听听你的决心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:47.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}支援者 你能向我发誓绝不会再犯同样的错误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是 我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}无论对贝尔大人 还是对赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}更重要的是对莉莉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉已经被贝尔大人救赎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}决不会背叛他 也不想背叛他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:05.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明白了 我暂且相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我告诉你实话吧 支援者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是理所当然的吧 三番五次欺骗贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}现在还想拉拢他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你还真是个讨人厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还有从刚才起 你那张丧气脸是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}肯定是因为贝尔对你太体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一点也不责备你 被自己的强烈罪恶感压得要崩溃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}用我的话来说 那只不过是撒娇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:43.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}既然如此 那么让我代替贝尔惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请帮我照顾贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:01.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}派你看着贝尔 不要被奇怪的家伙盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}事先声明 这不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}通过这件事 我确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:12.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}置之不理的话 贝尔还会受骗上当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:18.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}况且罪恶感归根究底也只不过是能否原谅自己的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果你想洗心革面 就用行动证明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有关组队的请求 我允许了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那孩子就交给你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:36.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}千万不要做出格的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:37.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}久等了 对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么 让我再次自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}初次见面 支援者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我 的 贝尔 拜托你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:55.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}慢吞吞后面来的 别妄想抢走属于我的贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这只偷腥猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不不 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:09.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人一直都对我很体贴温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要是为了贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:16.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不管对手是神明还是什么 我都会勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 绝不会认输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对了 我和埃伊娜小姐有约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}因为你的错 让贝尔逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你说什么 我再不会听神明大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\pos(640,53)}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:43.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个…埃伊娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:43.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等等…贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:03.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10} 突然逃跑是很没礼貌的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么她会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}华伦斯坦小姐 好像有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}之前在地下城遭到食人魔袭击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你离开后 我发现你掉了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:36.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一直想找机会还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这么说…那时候救了我的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我一直想对你说声抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:52.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}由于我失手放跑的米诺陶洛斯 让你受到很多伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}根本与华伦斯坦小姐无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}倒不如说是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:08.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}说对不起的人应该是没有道谢却接连落荒而逃的我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:28.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有关地下城的探索 你一直很努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:32.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这么短时间内就能到达第10层 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我还远远不够强 根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}战斗方式也如同外行人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:44.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还远远达不到自己定下的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}完全不行 呃…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:52.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没有人教你战斗方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:01.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么 我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么 华伦斯坦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:15.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}叫我艾丝就行了 大家都这么称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:21.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:31.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}话说有关训练 我该做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:37.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}从昨天起 我就一直在考虑该怎么教你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你用的武器是短刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}用踢腿或柔术攻击敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}短刀借我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:56.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝小姐 难道是天然呆？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:05.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个…重新整理一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}果然艾丝小姐是天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:22.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没关系 不是艾丝小姐的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们还是对战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就像你刚才的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}之后的战斗中 体会有各种经验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如此一来 就算你讨厌也一定会牢记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}保护自己虽是懦弱的表现 但也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但除此之外 你依然在害怕些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不能鲁莽乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不能制造死角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:24.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一击致命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:43.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}技巧之类的灵活运用 你还需要稍作加强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:22.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要想实现那位大人的夙愿 这点程度显然不够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}貌似有点能耐 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}很好 就挑你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看你怎么使用这把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 今天打算去到哪层呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:20.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 因为明天休息 今天想尽量下潜得深一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 因为我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没什么 寄宿的地方有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}再说我也有事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:37.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人为什么最近来地下城之前 遍体鳞伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:39.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:12.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}视野要开阔 不能出现死角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}数量有点多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}需要暂时撤退 调整战术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果一直这样害怕 我何时才能赶上她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我一定要追上她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起 我又晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我能问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么你的能力提高得那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我…一点也不厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实只不过…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}因为心中有一个无论如何想追赶上的她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:17:00.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还有一个不管发生任何事都想到达的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:07.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗 我也能明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}进行午睡的特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:28.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在地下城需要做到无论何时何地都能睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:33.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请问…难道你困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:35.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:40.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:41.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这就是一级冒险者的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}去吧 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:07.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}男人就该趁她睡着时 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:16.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么能放弃这种绝佳机会 她可能还翘首期待你接近她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等等 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我不记得教过你可以趁人睡着时偷袭他人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我绝不饶恕你亲吻她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赶快离开她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}之后是属于男人的内心争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:51.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝小姐 我们这是去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:33.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}应该肚子饿了吧 我们去吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不用在意 我也觉得饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}两个奶油红豆味炸土豆饼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多奶油 红豆双倍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:00.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你真是的 一个接一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:09.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}最后 终于偏偏…找上这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对…对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:21.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这么说 还剩最后两天？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:22.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:27.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}本来约定训练到洛基眷族远征之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}拜托你了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:36.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}知道了 既然说到这个份上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不过华伦某某人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果背着我对贝尔做些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}约定立即作废 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}绝对不能色诱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:48.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么
